review_text:
Regularly order from PLT with no issues however on this occasion the service has been shocking.  I’m still awaiting the remaining refund for an item returned in  January.  Ive been told at least 3 times it’s being reviewed and will be sorted, yesterday was the last day to expect it and again it’s not been refunded. shambles!! 
Have asked to raised a formal complaint as this is unacceptable and this hasn’t happened!
@prettylittlething sort it out!!
